# Private agent config (always excluded — see ~/.agents/flows/REPO.md).
# No trailing slash on purpose: `dotagents link` makes .agents a symlink, which git
# treats as a file, so a directory-only `.agents/` would NOT ignore it.
# *.local.md is the unshared override (machine- or user-specific) — it takes
# precedence over its non-local sibling and must never be committed.
.agents
*.local.md
CLAUDE*
.claude

# Build/dist output and generated docs site
build/
dist/
site/

